  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Covid for the President of the United States",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US President Joe Biden has tested positive for Covid-19 and is experiencing very mild symptoms, the White House said.",
        "The President is fully vaccinated and claims to have received two Covid-19 booster shots.",
        "Currently, there is a spread of the Omicron variant of Covid-19 in the United States, and the spread of the virus has also increased in the European region.",
        "The World Health Organization also recently warned of the latest outbreak of the epidemic, urging countries to refocus on face masks, social distancing and gathering in well-ventilated areas."
      ],
